               At Advanced Blast Protection we aspire to be the industry's leading developer of innovative armor and protection products. Our primary mission is to protect and save lives and we accomplish this by providing combat proven products, responsive engineering, on-time delivery, and outstanding product support. We measure our success in "lives saved" and believe that our reputation is our most important commodity. This philosophy frames our approach to all of our business activities. "Resolved to protect, engineered to defend."
