Insider Activity


Individual




James L. Pavitt



Mr. James L. Pavitt is President & Partner at JLP & Associates LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at CACI International, Inc., Advanced Blast Protection, Inc. and Patriot Defense Group LLC. Mr. Pavitt was previously employed as Deputy Director-Operations by Central Intelligence Agency (United States) and Executive Partner-Intelligence by Torch Hill Investment Partners LLC. He also served on the board at Cub Energy, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Missouri.



